                  h3 Intercept<sup><span class="font-copyright">&reg;</span></sup> Incubator
                  p Centrally managed Startup platform
                  p For Incubators to empower their members with Business Planning and Financial Modeling
          div(class="col-sm-6 col-md-4")
            a(href="/library")
              div.thumbnail.product-thumbnail(style="text-align: center;")
                i.fa.fa-book.fa-4x
                div.caption.white
                  h3 Intercept<sup><span class="font-copyright">&reg;</span></sup> Library
                  p Integrated Business Development
                  p For libraries
          div(class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-md-offset-4")
            a(href="/nonprofit").disabled
              div.thumbnail.product-thumbnail(style="text-align: center;")
                i.fa.fa-share-alt.fa-4x
                div.caption.white
                  h3 Intercept<sup><span class="font-copyright">&reg;</span></sup> NonProfit
                  h4 Coming Soon
